&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &apos;Gentium Plus&apos;;&quot;&gt;The Crucifixion along with the two thieves, the two Marys standing under the cross, Jesus being taken down from the Cross and buried, and the Resurrection.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
