&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;The Sacrifice of Isaac: on the right Abraham prays asking God to annul this terrible decree, while on the left he is raising the knife when his gaze is guided by the angel towards the ram which he his commanded to offer in Isaac&apos;s stead.&amp;#160; (Genesis 22)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
