&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Maimonides&apos; amazing life story starts in the multicultural world of Cordoba and ends in the King&apos;s court in Cairo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Photo: an official medal of the state of Israel, honoring Maimonides&apos; 800th birthday, showing the various stations of Maimonides life across the Mediterranean.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
