&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 14.2pt; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background: white;&quot;&gt;After Maimonides&apos; death the manuscript remained in the hands of the family in Egypt for several generations. When in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;RTL&quot; style=&quot; font-family: &apos;Gentium Plus&apos;; background: white;&quot;&gt;1375&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background: white;&quot;&gt;, due to the persecutions of Jews in Egypt, &amp;#160;the descendants of Maimonides moved to Aleppo in Syria&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

