--&gt;
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The girdle that binds it, and an embroidered mantle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or alternatively, a case that covers it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
