--&gt;
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 53.45pt;&quot;&gt;In 1942 Yahuda received a position in the New School of Social Research in New-York, and from then on, until his death in 1951, spent most of his time on his research.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 53.45pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

